{"tid":1297002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲可以開解我","createTime":"2019-07-08T13:58:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T14:17:40.000Z","uid":164241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"970dc03df14678429ae22f59b95c99d7fb484973","tid":1297002,"uid":164241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T13:58:36.000Z","msg":"經歷抗爭過後,我返到工作崗位,但呢幾日我真係:無嘢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同事之間呢排圍繞住:<br />\n後生仔千期唔好搞政治，無好後果下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n出得嚟行頭𠴱班肯定收咗錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n廢青朋友仲話想如過可以嫌不得攞支槍打爆佢哋個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n阻住佢肯定會篤盡油車埋去<br />\n<br />\n的士佬on99走埋去送死，我心諗的士佬都有義氣過你哋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好感激,多謝義士佢哋,每位巴打每次出嚟抗爭大家一齊幫忙,保護,互相協助逃忙好留戀同你哋一齊相處嘅時光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以教我如何處理目前嘅困局，如何面對呢班割蓆，篤灰，各家自掃門前雪，藍得很嘅藍戰士，廢老，廢青同事呢？<br />\n<br />\n可能你會話：咪劈炮囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我何嘗無諗過呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但無奈地家中仲有年邁嘅媽媽要供養照顧，真係等錢開飯咁嘅款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好辛苦,好困惑,看不透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93082dedf1ba36418c5324cdcd2c26b82fdb6ecc","tid":1297002,"uid":276293,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T14:17:40.000Z","msg":"長遠: 積極搵工 別無他法<br />\n短期: 工事以外不傾談 話不投機半句多"}]}